description: UAPC, Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and production of oil and gas properties in the United States. It also provides operational services to third party well owners in Austin, Texas. The company was formerly known as United American Petroleum Corp. and changed its name to UAPC, Inc. in August 2020. UAPC, Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Longwood, Florida.
